public class YanceesJmDNSService
extends edu.uci.isr.yancees.server.service.AbstractService

A Yancees plug in for JmDNS 1.0RC2, based on Roberto's code This service connects YANCESS with its peers in a subnetwork. It uses the service location protocol (SLP)

publishToPeers

public void publishToPeers(edu.uci.isr.yancees.EventInterface evt)
Propagates, or publishes an event in all the peers of the network. Note that for this operation, we do not use the regular publishing interface of YANCEES as a way to prevent repeated circular publishing of events.

Parameters:
evt - is the event to be propagated to the other peers.
